                  <li>Offsetting refrigeration loads</li>
                  <li>Rapid payback period</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Cold storage facility in Geelong's western industrial zone.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-item bento-wide-top">
